  </title>
  <description type="2" xml:lang="EN">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project objective is to identify innovative mechanisms of Blended Finance that can be used to dramatically scale-up investment in sustainable infrastructure projects that are aligned with national development priorities of participating governments, achieve their Nationally Determined Contributions (NDCs) under the Paris Agreement and address the Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs). The overarching goal is to assist developing countries in becoming aid-independent.</narrative>
